{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "/nodes/vop/DASH--build_attribute_array-1.0/DASH-build_attribute_array-icon.svg", "type": "node", "context": "vop", "internal": "build_attribute_array", "version": "1.0", "namespace": "DASH"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Build Attribute Array"], "extent": [52, 78]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Given an array of elements' ids, source the attribute value for each element into an array."], "extent": [78, 178]}, {"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [178, 184], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["If the chosen attribute is already of type array, the multiple sourced arrays will be flattened in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["values"]}]}, " output. The ", {"type": "ui", "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["sources"]}]}, " output can be used to assess where did the value came from."], "extent": [184, 391]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 1, "id": "inputs", "container": true, "type": "inputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [391, 399], "body": [{"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["elements"]}], "extent": [399, 412], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Array of geometry elements' ids that should match the class set in ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Class"]}, " and exist in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Geometry"]}, " in order to correctly get and append the element value to the array."], "extent": [412, 593]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "text": "Inputs"}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [593, 605], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Geometry"], "extent": [605, 616], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Source geometry to query."], "extent": [634, 665]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["opinput:#"]}, " will either source from an Attribute VOP input or from any valid spare input going up the node hierarchy. The default is the first input."], "extent": [665, 821]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["op:/../.."]}, " will source from a node path. Must have geometry."], "extent": [821, 889]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"type": "code", "text": ["/../.."]}, " location on disk of a geometry file. Supports environment variables, like ", {"type": "code", "text": ["$HOME"]}, ", ", {"type": "code", "text": ["$JOB"]}, ", ", {"type": "code", "text": ["$HIP"]}, ", etc."], "extent": [889, 1009]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "geometry"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Attribute"], "extent": [1009, 1020], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Name of attribute to import as array."], "extent": [1039, 1086]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Given a valid ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Geometry"]}, ", this drop-down menu lists its attributes sorted by data type, divided by class. Using the menu will automatically set ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Class"]}, " and ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Data Type"]}, " to match the picked attribute."], "extent": [1086, 1296]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "attribute"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Class"], "extent": [1296, 1303], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Class of attribute to import. Automatically set by ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Attribute"]}, "."], "extent": [1318, 1389]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "class"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Data Type"], "extent": [1389, 1400], "body": [{"typ